<page title="Download">
  <section title="Playable Versions - Stable">
    <subsection title="Windows">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://pingus.googlecode.com/files/Pingus-0.7.6.exe">Pingus-0.7.6.exe</a> [16 Mb]<br />
        </li>
      </ul>
    </subsection>

    <subsection title="MacOSX (outdated)">
      <p>There are two unofficial ports to MacOSX of older versions of
      Pingus. There is currently no MacOSX port of the latest
      version</p>
      <ul>
         <li><a href="http://www.apple.com/downloads/macosx/games/cards_puzzle/pingus.html">Pingus 0.7.2 for Intel Macs</a> [15MB]</li>
         <li><a href="http://community.games4mac.de/index.php?showtopic=17290">Pingus 0.7.0 for PPC Macs</a> [60MB]</li>
      </ul>
    </subsection>

    <subsection title="Linux / Source">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://pingus.googlecode.com/files/pingus-0.7.6.tar.bz2">pingus-0.7.6.tar.bz2</a>
          [13 MB]<br />
        </li>
      </ul>
    </subsection>
  </section>

  <section title="Development Versions">
    <p>The Git tree can be checked out via:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><tt>git clone https://code.google.com/p/pingus/</tt></li>
    </ul>

    <p>The Google Code project page can be found at:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/pingus/">http://code.google.com/p/pingus/</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section title="Old Stuff">
    <p>Older released can be found at:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="ftp://pingus.seul.org/pub/pingus/">ftp://pingus.seul.org/pub/pingus/</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
